==Hindi==
===Etymology===
From Prakrit जीवो and Sanskrit जीवः

===Noun===
'''जी''' (jī) {{m}}
# a form of address, a term of endearment or respect, Sir, Master, Madam
# [[yes]] (short for जी [[हाँ]])
# Life, soul, self, spirit, mind
# heart; courage; disposition; affection, regard; strength, health

